  "comments": [],
  "completed": false,
  "dialogue": [
    {
      "content": "老师早啊，怎么都不来找我呀？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:56",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "难道是因为昨天我们讲了蒋介石笑话，你被抓走了吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:56"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhhhh",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:56"
    },
    {
      "content": "你是在关心我，还是在诅咒我？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:57"
    },
    {
      "content": "昨天你说你换班了，早上发信息给你又没人回",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:57"
    },
    {
      "content": "想着我中午忙完了再给你发信息",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:57"
    },
    {
      "content": "我发现你很擅长解释啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:58"
    },
    {
      "content": "你不觉得解释可以让人和人之间少很多误会吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:58"
    },
    {
      "content": "多点解释，少点误会。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:58"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhhh又爆金句是吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:59"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhhhh笑死了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:59"
    },
    {
      "content": "那你推荐我去参加奇葩说吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:59"
    },
    {
      "content": "笑死，我怎么推荐你？我是马东女儿吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:00"
    },
    {
      "content": "你可以天天在马东的微博下留言，以及拉着你其他的朋友，同学，亲戚帮我留言",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:00"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhhhh",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:00"
    },
    {
      "content": "真的假的？你想上奇葩说？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:01"
    },
    {
      "content": "开玩笑，我好像不擅长和人吵架",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:01"
    },
    {
      "content": "但我但我很乐意看着奇葩选手吵架",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:01"
    },
    {
      "content": "那么没道理的东西都能炒出花来。又给了我活下去的很强大自信啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:02"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhhh笑死了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:02"
    },
    {
      "content": "我还记得肖骁",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:02"
    },
    {
      "content": "哎，你还记得姜思达吗？",
