      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:06"
    },
    {
      "content": "万一张思达是柏拉图呢",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:06"
    },
    {
      "content": "那真的别逗你姜哥笑了",
